name: LogFilter
description: The output log level of the SDK.

parameters.Off: 0: Do not output any log information.

parameters.Debug: 0x080f: Output all log information. Set your log filter as DEBUG if you want to get the most complete log file.

parameters.Info: 0x000f: Output CRITICAL, ERROR, WARNING, and INFO level log information. We recommend setting your log filter as this level.

parameters.Warning: 0x000e: Output CRITICAL, ERROR, and WARNING level log information.

parameters.Error: 0x000c: Output CRITICAL and ERROR level log information.
